As of the 2010 census, Wacissa had a population of 386 and 197 housing units.<ref name="Census 2010"/>

The Wacissa Census Designated Place (CDP) had a population of 418 and 215 housing units as of July 1, 2021.<ref>[https://florida.hometownlocator.com/fl/jefferson/wacissa.cfm Florida home town locator]</ref>

